tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE panel_rating (
    panel_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    manufacturer_id INT NOT NULL,
    efficiency_rating DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    production_year INT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (manufacturer_id) REFERENCES panel_manufacturer(manufacturer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE panel_location (
    location_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    panel_id INT NOT NULL,
    installation_date DATE NOT NULL,
    location_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (panel_id) REFERENCES panel_rating(panel_id)
);

CREATE TABLE panel_performance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    panel_id INT NOT NULL,
    performance_date DATE NOT NULL,
    efficiency_measurement DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (panel_id) REFERENCES panel_rating(panel_id)
);

CREATE TABLE SolarPanelEfficiencyRatings (
    panel_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    efficiency_rating FLOAT,
    installation_date DATE,
    manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
    country_of_origin VARCHAR(255)
)
